room_title: Escape room "Franklin's Miscalculation" by Escape Entertainment in Philadelphia
review: The escape we chose, Time Trap, was particularly challenging (from what were told, only 25% of people manage to escape!), but it was well thought out and loads of fun!! Great time was had by all!!

room_title: Escape room "Franklin's Miscalculation" by Escape Entertainment in Philadelphia
review: One of the best escape rooms we've done! Staff was friendly and helpful! Prohibition Pandemonium room was challenging but not impossible, very fun. Time Trap was very difficult but loads of fun as well. Looking forward to coming back for Philadelphia Phrenzy! Thank you Katie for everything!

room_title: Escape room "Franklin's Miscalculation" by Escape Entertainment in Philadelphia
review: Best escape room that I have been to in Philadelphia! I did the time warp room today and it was tough but a lot of fun!! The place is very clean and the staff was wonderful.
